鐵車廂扶手的細菌有地域性分布，當中唯一連接深圳關口的東鐵線，其耐藥性細菌的含量是眾多線路中最高。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學者指出，這些耐藥性細菌多存在於內地豬場飼料中，並易於珠江三角洲地區的土壤中找到</span></span>，繼而透過東鐵線「跨境」到港。<br />\n<br />\n研究又提醒，在東鐵線扶手發現的細菌基因，會對四環素等抗生素呈抗藥性，日後細菌可能會變成多重耐藥的生物，即「超級細菌」。研究人員認為是次研究，可幫助政府制定公共衛生計劃，以阻止城市之間的疾病傳播。"},{"pid":"fd31dfed5c710c6d7579a32331574d7d0f80f8f0","tid":1074572,"uid":58320,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"D畫風同上色咁撚似一個大陸插畫師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88656eaf9f0dd75ce35245c792065bfe919d688d","tid":1074572,"uid":118080,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"76d4b4565ee6687c544b7f88456e75a792623951","tid":1074572,"uid":55533,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"觀塘線=綜援新移民公屋仔<br />\n荃灣線=雞蟲阿叔<br />\n港島線=串到仆街但有錢既西裝友<br />\n南港島=有錢鬼佬/abc仔<br />\n西鐵線=圍頭佬牛屎佬，得閒就返大陸叫雞<br />\n馬鐵=短撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"馬鐵正解，男人坐馬鐵姐係自認細jer仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ae461e61e784ca3adff1411bab05f547b95fe9","tid":1074572,"uid":59140,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"92a12d66556b6a349dcb2555d738408a0b30e409","tid":1074572,"uid":118080,"like":5,"dislike":113,"score":-108,"quote":{"pid":"a6703f8d16aad153d6bde4c46fb95db9919de7ba","tid":1074572,"uid":196924,"like":259,"dislike":8,"score":251,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"東　鐵　唔　撚　係　地　鐵　線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過google話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EszEMac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEszEMac.png&h=fd5d5787&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"Google話乜 你就要信架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"